  "body": "# Rationale\r\n\r\nMany administrators often forget to update geth, resulting in version differences and inability to synchronize. I suggest adding 2 parameter optimizations.\r\n-update Update latest stable version from https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/releases , verify Signature.\r\n-auto-update , the parameter is the seconds for regular updates, the default is 86400 * 7, if this function is added, it may take 2 processes.\r\nI suggest that we introduce -update first to help administrators update more conveniently.\r\n\r\n# Implementation\r\nFirst check https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/releases , if there is an update, then download the file and signature form https://gethstore.blob.core.windows.net/builds/, verify the signature, update.\r\n\r\nI can implement this feature.",
