    "body": "There are lots of things to consider here, also, a lot of people run via docker. In some ways, docker already provides \"manual auto-update\", so us adding it explicitly to geth just makes things even more complicated. \r\n\r\nDoing it via docker is something like: \r\n```\r\ndocker stop -t120 geth && docker pull ethereum/client-go:latest && docker start geth\r\n```\r\n",
